S.FORM: Jordan Gaga kska Yacow ka Jordan, 31 00 N, 36 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 89,342 sq km(hangan na o Tg112)(knlbanga dxgal o 88,802 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 540 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 8,185,384 hiyi. Gaga Amman ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 25 idas 5 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Jordan ga wada sugan 11.40 ka dxgal qpahan, 1.10 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 87.50 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Abdullah II of Jordan, pnaah hngkawas1999 idas 2 jiyax 7pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
